metadata.name: QUEEN OF OCEANS
metadata.description: "In her Ocean Of Dreams, she sailed herself as the Queen of the Ocean." She is Atlanna, the rebelous Queen of the Oceans. Tempestous as the Oceans and stronger than the foundations of the Earth. She rules over the sister race of humans, The Atlanteans, an underwater species of amphibious humanoids that inhabit the Earth's oceans and are native to the kingdom of Atlantis.
